# Qwen2.5-VL ChartQA Demo

Upload a chart, ask a concise question, and compare the Qwen2.5-VL-3B base model with the hardmix ChartQA QLoRA adapter.

The adapter improved relaxed accuracy from 75.94% to 77.86% on the complete ChartQA validation split. See the project README for evaluation details and limitations.

Required Space variable:

```text
CHARTQA_ADAPTER_PATH=<HUGGING_FACE_ADAPTER_REPO>
```

Optional variables:

```text
CHARTQA_MODEL_ID=Qwen/Qwen2.5-VL-3B-Instruct
CHARTQA_LOAD_IN_4BIT=1
CHARTQA_MIN_PIXELS=50176
CHARTQA_MAX_PIXELS=401408
```

Deploy the complete project repository and use this file as the Space repository root `README.md`.
